verbose_text: Cap dependent protein translation is mediated by eIF4F, a eukaryotic initiation factor complex composed of the cap binding protein eIF4E; the RNA helicase eIF4A; and the scaffold protein eIF4G, which interacts with eIF4E and eIF4A.
evidence: translation is mediated by eIF4F, a eukaryotic initiation factor complex composed of the cap-binding protein eIF4E; the RNA helicase eIF4A
